data.description: Are you looking for that little piece of country living, look no further that is what you will find here. Brick home with a partially finished basement, also includes a 3 car detached garage setting on approximately 2 ac that is surrounded by pasture land. Home offers 3 bedroom and 1 bath on the main level along with a kitchen, dining room and living room. Fantastic back deck offering great country views, perfect for cookouts and relaxing with a cup of coffee in the morning. Take the spiral stairs to the basement where you have a  large room that could be a bedroom or office just whatever you want it can be, 2nd bathroom & laundry room. 1 car garage, with lots of extra storage.  13 month home warranty for peace of mind.
